</SP>
<SP>
<PB N="197" REF="025384_0196_0FCD114C5A216078">
<SPEAKER>Yo. &s;i&s;t.</SPEAKER>
<P>There is no need to afflict your&s;elf now, Sir, about it <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> my &s;i&s;ter, is delivered another way, Sir, and the thing is over.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Fa.</SPEAKER>
<P>But I am a warning to all parents, that have the good of their children at heart, never to make light of &s;uch things, but &s;earch them to the bottom; and the more their children depend upon them, the greater is their o|bligation to be very careful.</P>
